#' @param t0 integer, start iteration at t = t0.
#' @param y \eqn{(m, N)} matrix with the observed outputs \eqn{(y_1,...,y_N}{(y[1],...,y[N])}.
#' @param u \eqn{(m, N)} matrix. This matrix is **overwritten** with the computed
